      "title": "Gazette issued to maintain Public Security Ordinance",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A gazette notification was issued yesterday calling on all the members of the armed forces to maintain the Public Security Ordinance with effect from Monday (22).",
        "The gazette notification was issued by President Ranil Wickremesinghe. (Chaturanga Samarawickrama)"
      ],
